Copa Ciudad Viña del Mar 1976-2005

Traditional summer tournament held in Viña del Mar, Chile.
The tournament changed name several times.
Palmares

Year Winners
1976 Fluminense (Rio de Janeiro)
1978 Internacional (Porto Alegre)
1992 Universidad de Chile
1993 Everton
1994   not held
1995 Everton
1996   not held
1997   not held
1998 Colo Colo
2000 América de Cali
Copa Viva Viña
2001 Internacional (Porto Alegre)
2002 Universidad Católica
2003   not held
Copa Gato-Viña del Mar
2004 Universidad de Chile
Copa Verano
2005 Olimpia (Asunción)
1976

Participants;
 
